import {gql} from '@apollo/client'

export const ORDERS=gql`
query QUery($ouser_id: ID!) {
    orders(ouser_id: $ouser_id) {
      ouser_id
      oproduct_id {
        _id
        productname
        price
        shopname
        image
        category
        description
        count
        
        sales
      }
      oquantity
      odate
      checked
    }
    
  }`
